This document reports statistics and graphs from city-level averages pollution data form CPCB:

  1. summary statistics for all pollutants using original data (not censored)
  2. summary statistics for all pollutants using censored data
  3. plots of PM2.5 using original data (not censored) for some cities
  4. plots of PM2.5 using censored data for some cities
